118			Short: "Gracefully stop running agent workers",
119			Long: `Gracefully terminate one or more running agent workers.
120	
121	The server sends SIGTERM to the worker's process group, waits for the configured
122	grace window, and escalates to SIGKILL if the leader is still alive. The worker's
123	bead claim is released and a bead.stopped event is appended to the tracker before
124	the kill, so claims are not leaked even when the full grace elapses.
125	
126	Examples:
127	  ddx agent workers stop worker-20260418T100000-abcd
128	  ddx agent workers stop --all-over 1h
129	  ddx agent workers stop --state running
130	  ddx agent workers stop --bead ddx-abc12345`,
